                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 9.1: 2"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/28/chapter-9.1">
                                Chapter 9.1: 2
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">970</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>At the age of 28, I’m still single, just like during 27 years before.

Being single is not scary, the big problem is while you still want to stay single, your mom keeps urging you to get married.

Aka FA&#039;s story…

Original Webcomic
Official English: INKR </p>
