                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="92197" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kenka-raamen" title="Kenka Raamen">
                                <img alt="Kenka Raamen"
                                     class="lazy"
                                     src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/kenka-raamen.webp"
                                     data-src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/kenka-raamen.webp"
                                     width="120" height="170"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     >
                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kenka-raamen"
                                    title="Kenka Raamen">Kenka Raamen</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 162: Vol.17 CHAPTER 11: SOY SAUCE RAMEN"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kenka-raamen/chapter-162">
                                Chapter 162: Vol.17 CHAPTER 11: SOY SAUCE RAMEN
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">880</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>In this passionate gourmet comic, ex-bikie gang leader Yoshitsune Genda faces off with his rivals in the world of ramen. Each encounter brings him closer to ramen mastery. His father, owner and chef of the struggling Gantetsu Ramen, uses his bare hands to lift ramen out of boiling water. For Yoshitsune, the leader of the Salamander Gang, every day is one brawl after another. One day he meets the fiery Remi, who lures him into a contract negotiation to sell his father&#039;s ramen shop! What will happen to
Yoshitsune!? </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kenka-raamen" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="92196" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide" title="Kei-chan, Damette Iwanaide">
                                <img alt="Kei-chan, Damette Iwanaide"
                                     class="lazy"
                                     src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide.webp"
                                     data-src="https://img-r2.2xstorage.com/thumb/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide.webp"
                                     width="120" height="170"
                                     loading="lazy"
                                     >
                            </a>
                            <h3>
                                <a href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide"
                                    title="Kei-chan, Damette Iwanaide">Kei-chan, Damette Iwanaide</a>
                            </h3>

                            
                                                                                    <a class="list-story-item-wrap-chapter" title="Chapter 1"
                                href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide/chapter-1">
                                Chapter 1
                            </a>
                            
                            
                            <div><span class="aye_icon">242</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>High school teacher Kei has never been in a relationship his entire life. Toma, his next-door neighbor and student, is like family to him, but they&#039;ve grown distant over the years, much to Kei&#039;s secret disappointment.

One day, Toma accidentally learns that Kei is actually interested in guys. All of a sudden, Toma&#039;s aloof attitude takes a 180 as he starts to put the moves on Kei... Toma even confesses that he&#039;s always been in love with him! There&#039;s no stopping Toma&#039;s advances! This is a naughty and heart-pounding romance between a handsome high school student living next door and a teacher who&#039;s a beginner in love! </p>
                              <div class="read-more-wrap">
                                <a class="read-more" href="https://www.mangabats.com/manga/kei-chan-damette-iwanaide" title>Read more</a>
                              </div>
                                                    </div>

                        
                        
                                                                    
                        <div class="list-comic-item-wrap">
                            <a data-id="92194" class="list-story-item bookmark_check cover"
