                                                          <p>Kuroitsu Tohka is a research assistant at the Monster Develoment Department of the evil organization Agastia. However, the enemies she must fight at present are not heroes. &quot;Problems just before a presentation at a big meeting&quot;, &quot;Proposals thrown together in ten minutes&quot;, &quot;Impossible demands from the higher-ups&quot;... As long as there is good in this world, there will also be evil. </p>
