                                                          <p>This new line of Edu-Manga features Astro Boy, one of Japan&#039;s most popular icons among children who journeys alongside the reader. He provides for kids not only a history lesson but also a richer understanding of the life lessons these historical figures share with us.

Jeanne d&#039;Arc is the 15th century national heroine of France. From Napoleon to the present, French politicians of all leanings have invoked her memory. She was beatified in 1909 and canonized as a saint in 1920.

Note: Edu-Manga is a term coined in Japan which means Educational Manga. </p>
