                            <div><span class="aye_icon">825</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Of all the things to wake up as, a squirrel is the last thing she expected. Sure, she’s technically a divine beast from a novel, but she’s a squirrel all the same. Determined to make the best of it, Momo—Inky—whatever her name is now—gets to work. And while she thought a little kindness would be enough to keep Yohan from villainy, she didn’t think it would lead to a new human life as Yurika, a caring family, love... or the kind of secrets that could change everything the world has ever known. </p>
