                                                          <p>After being abandoned in the mountains, I started enjoying a carefree camping lifeonly to end up accidentally racking up some unbelievable achievements! As I tamed holy beasts and dominated every challenge, the ones who cast me out began to fall apart on their own… And for some reason, now I&#039;m suddenly super popular!? A thrilling comeuppance fantasy packed with harem antics and gourmet adventures! </p>
