                            <div><span class="aye_icon">100</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>&quot;A love so deep, I’d give up everything&quot;... A time-loop romance between two clumsy souls Olivia, a duke’s daughter, was condemned as a villainess by her fiancé, Crown Prince Luminous. But when she came to, she found time had rewound to before the incident. In her first life, jealousy had turned her love for him into hatred, leading both her beloved and her family to ruin. &quot;In this second life... I won&#039;t get love wrong.&quot; Though she resolves to ensure everyone&#039;s happiness, she finds herself shaken by a side of Luminous she has never seen before, a love tinged with strong possessive desire. </p>
