                            <div><span class="aye_icon">158</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>Iris Scarlet and the second prince, Johann, shared a loving marriage despite it being a political arrangement. However, their relationship fractured when a merchant’s daughter named Dolores appeared and used a mysterious power to captivate Johann. After becoming his second wife, Dolores framed Iris for a crime she did not commit, leading to Iris’s execution.

Vowing to avoid the same tragic fate, Iris wakes up in the past to begin her second life. This time, a powerfully named Ron from the wolf tribe appears to aid her. Armed with a dependable partner, Iris embarks on a romance fantasy driven by revenge to change her destiny. </p>
