                            <div><span class="aye_icon">883</span></div> <br><br>

                            
                                                          <p>During one summer in her teens, Erika’s mother pressured her into going to a local overnight camp. Despite her reservations, Erika ended up meeting a girl named Emi... and Emi didn&#039;t let Erika’s anti-social front prevent them from forming a special bond.

Now in their 30s, Erika and Emi reminisce about that fateful summer and consider what could have been. </p>
